<h2> The Yurts at Pacific Trails </h2>

<dt><strong><p> What is a yurt? </p></dt></strong>
<dd><p> Our luxuary yurts are permanet structures four feet off the ground. Each yurt is fully enclosed wih canvas walls, a wooden floor, and a roof dome that can be opend.</p></dd>

<dt><strong><p> How are the yurts furnished? </p></dt></strong>
<dd><p> Each yurt is funished with a queen-size bed with down quilt and gas-fired stove. Your luxury camping experience includes electricity and a sin with hot and cold runnig water. Shower and restroom facilities are located in the lodge. </p></dd>

<dt><strong><p> What should I bring? </p></dt></strong>
<dd><p> Most guests pack comfort walking shoes and plan to dress for changing weather with light layers of clothing. It's also helpful to bringa flashlight and sense of adventure!</p></dd>


